					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Just in case it's unclear; I didn't see anyone else mention it.<br /><br />The NES can only produce 64 sprites on any given frame. This is either 64 or 128 tiles (depending if the double-height sprite mode is enabled).</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

